    "longBusinessSummary": "TienLen Steel Corporation Joint Stock Company engages in the trade of iron and steel products in Vietnam. It offers steel products, including steel sections, steel plates, hot rolled coils and plate, and building steel, as well as hot rolled checker steel coils and plates, Larssen sheet piles, I/H beam steel, construction steel, round bar steel, angle steel, channel steel, rail steel, and other steel. The company also leases steel piles, plates, sections, etc. for construction of bridges and roads; and leases factories/warehouses and offices. In addition, it engages in the wholesale of iron, steel, aluminum, and copper materials, as well as construction materials, timber, and processed wood; cargo handling, construction of house; ground preparation; installation of other construction system; road transportation of goods; mechanical processing, handling, and mechanical processing; warehousing and storage of goods; logistics services; and consulting, brokerage, real estate auction, and land use right auction business. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Bien Hoa City, Vietnam.",
